  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Wishing Stone is a captivating point & click puzzle adventure game with challenging puzzles and a mysterious visual novel storyline. The game features a touching family story that takes you on a journey with Ailsa, who unexpectedly receives a magical wishing stone from a suspicious witch. The stone can grant her three wishes, but the first wish must be made before midnight. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Ailsa embarks on a journey to regain her normalcy, she must explore the world, solve puzzles, and make important decisions that will determine her fate. With different choices and actions leading to various endings, the game offers a unique and unpredictable experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ailsa's life takes an unexpected turn when she receives the wishing stone. As she delves into its powers, she uncovers a world of contradictions and uncertainty. Is this all a terrible nightmare, or does something more sinister lurk beneath the surface?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As she explores and solves puzzles, Ailsa must navigate through a world that is not what it seems. Will she be able to uncover the truth, or will she succumb to the darkness? The fate of Ailsa's journey is in your hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/6a2bb6d940434965b0bdd6a7669c14d4.poster.avif?t=1771046052\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/6a2bb6d940434965b0bdd6a7669c14d4.webm?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/6a2bb6d940434965b0bdd6a7669c14d4.mp4?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore the environment to discover the life of Ailsa and find out what's happening around her. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/a801ecc69dcbd9d35929168503917b34.poster.avif?t=1771046052\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/a801ecc69dcbd9d35929168503917b34.webm?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/a801ecc69dcbd9d35929168503917b34.mp4?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Collect items and use items to interact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/1ff35e80e2c5c5c8f0c15b1948ee0df5.poster.avif?t=1771046052\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/1ff35e80e2c5c5c8f0c15b1948ee0df5.webm?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/1ff35e80e2c5c5c8f0c15b1948ee0df5.mp4?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Solve various fun puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/4215a579fa129565d4904593f561261f.poster.avif?t=1771046052\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/4215a579fa129565d4904593f561261f.webm?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/4215a579fa129565d4904593f561261f.mp4?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Read diaries, letters, notes and dive into Ailsa's past. Help her solve mysteries and find lost memories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/5c7a5dd173c571fce35297d81d42f720.poster.avif?t=1771046052\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/5c7a5dd173c571fce35297d81d42f720.webm?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1330100/extras/5c7a5dd173c571fce35297d81d42f720.mp4?t=1771046052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Experience a touching original story with twists and turns while listening to beautiful music. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Wishing Stone has 7 endings (excluding the 2 bad ends) + a special chapter.</p>",
